      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Experience the pinnacle of automotive excellence with this showroom-quality masterpiece. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, appearing as though it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, glass-like finish protected by a professional ceramic coating\u2014zero swirl marks, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of luxury, with premium leather that still carries that new-car scent and high-definition displays that remain crystal clear. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; every service has been performed ahead of schedule at certified dealerships, with a comprehensive binder of records included. From the pristine engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, every detail reflects a life of pampered ownership. This isn't just a used car; it is a collector-grade investment for the discerning driver who refuses to compromise.",
      "price": 48500.0,
